A FORMER BBC local radio DJ pleaded guilty to 41 sex offences against children. Roger Pond, 46, of Gillingham, Kent, also admitted taking indecent photographs of children. Pond, who worked for Radio Kent, was remanded in custody at Maidstone Crown Court.


